metadata.name: this place, once forgotten
metadata.description:
remembered again by the gods.



One god led his faith race down from the sky, one devil climbed out of the abyss.



The gods asked humans to sacrifice their souls and serve themselves as emotionless believers.



The devil has beguiled man into signing a contract, becoming the devil's apostle.



From that day on, mankind learned a cruel truth. It turned out that the gods were not as kind as they were told.
